{"tid":996802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個中同成日係度宣傳咩順勢療法, 師自己為醫師, 好ON9","createTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:37.000Z","uid":197350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1a80930085641abc64ee807e451bf82238eb16","tid":996802,"uid":197350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"有個中同讀完中五就去左讀IVE之類, 出黎做左幾年野, 上年就開始加入咩順勢療法協會, <br />\n日日係FACEBOOK講順勢療法點好點好, 得閒又POST D西藥副作用報導去彈西醫點樣冇用點樣醫唔倒人<br />\n仲稱自己係醫師, 可以幫人診症同用藥治療, 又話醫糖尿 濕疹等等, 連更年期都有得醫。<br />\n跟住走去GOOGLE下咩9野係順勢療法, ON9, 係咩200幾年前D人9UP撞中醫倒病就話掂。<br />\n話咩用某D物質溝水30轉 再飲就有效, 30轉呀!!, 咩物質都溝到冇晒啦ON9。<br />\n傷風感冒等到自己好返又當成功例子。中學時都已經覺得條女ON9, 咁多年冇變過。<br />\n唔信西醫既話, 我信中醫好過啦, 幾時輪到順勢療法<br />\n同幣少有咩差別, 都係圍埋一堆人自吹自擂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A1%BA%E5%8A%BF%E7%96%97%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A1%25BA%25E5%258A%25BF%25E7%2596%2597%25E6%25B3%2595&d=5OqtTyzK%2BQ7Li%2Bjn4kBC%2FkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a388a8bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A1%BA%E5%8A%BF%E7%96%97%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%BD%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E4%B9%8B%E9%A0%86%E5%8B%A2%E7%99%82%E6%B3%95-%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%86%E5%8B%A2%E7%99%82%E6%B3%95%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E5%89%B5%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%9D%9C%E5%AE%B6%E9%BA%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%25A0%2586%25E5%258B%25A2%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A0%2586%25E5%258B%25A2%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259D%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6